 with the staffers from different departments contracted the flu-like infection.\n\nSpokesperson Nepali further said, \u201cWe have issued a notice informing the public about the closure of the Metropolis office except for essential services due to Covid-19.\u201d\n\nLikewise, the Department of Livestock in the Metropolis has been closed indefinitely after its staffers had been infected with the coronavirus.","title":"Pokhara Metropolitan City shuts down all services except essential ones - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/20/143370/","video":[]}
